#: getTips.go:81
msgid ""
"%s is your gateway to Cloud Native - find your flock at [landscape.cncf.io]"
"(%s)"
msgstr ""
"%s est votre porte d'entrée au Cloud Native - trouvez votre vocation à "
"[landscape.cncf.io](%s)"

#: getTips.go:80
msgid ""
"%s is your gateway to Kubernetes 󱃾 `kind create cluster` to [get started](%s)"
msgstr ""
"%s est votre porte d'entrée à Kubernetes 󱃾 `kind create cluster` pour "
"[commencer](%s)"

#: getTips.go:82
msgid ""
"%s separates the OS from your development environment - embrace the cloud-"
"native workflow !"
msgstr ""
"%s sépare le système d'exploitation de l'environnement de développement - "
"prenez en mains le workflow cloud-native !"

#: getTips.go:107
msgid ""
"*%s isn't a distro*, this is a custom image built on  Fedora Atomic Desktop "
"technology ~ [View our mission](%s)"
msgstr ""
"*%s n'est pas une distribution*, mais une image custom créée à partir de la "
"technologie  Fedora Atomic ~ [Voir notre mission](%s)"

#: getTips.go:109
msgid ""
"**H.264 hardware acceleration is supported out of the box.** No tweaks "
"necessary!"
msgstr ""
"**L'accélération matérielle H.264 est prise en charge par défaut.** Aucun "
"réglage nécessaire !"

#: getTips.go:34
msgid "**Protect your video games!** ~ [Visit Stop Killing Games](%s)"
msgstr ""
"**Protégez les jeux auxquels vous jouez !** ~ [Découvrez Stop Killing Games]"
"(%s)"

#: getTips.go:108
msgid ""
"**Support indie game preservation and OSS developers!** ~ [Join Hit Save!'s "
"Patreon](%s)"
msgstr ""
"**Soutenez la préservation de jeux indépendants et des développeurs de "
"l'Open-Source !** ~ [Rejoignez le Patreon de Hit Save!](%s)"

#: getTips.go:91
msgid ""
"*Confused about what games are compatible with Linux?* The `ProtonDB Badges` "
"plugin for Decky Loader adds community-powered game compatibility badges to "
"your entire 󰓓 Steam Library ~ [More info](%s)"
msgstr ""
"*Confus par la compatibilité de vos jeux avec Linux ?* Le plugin Decky "
"Loader pour les badges `ProtonDB` rajoute des badges de compatibilité gérés "
"par la communauté pour toute votre bibliothèque 󰓓 Steam ~ [Plus d'infos](%s)"

#: getTips.go:90
msgid ""
"*Games missing icons?* The `SteamGridDB` plugin for Decky Loader makes it "
"easy to add missing art ~ [More info](%s)"
msgstr ""
"*Des icônes manquantes pour vos jeux?* Le plugin Decky Loader `SteamGridDB` "
"rend accessible l'ajout de couvertures et de bannières pour vos jeux ~ [Plus "
"d'infos](%s)"

#: getTips.go:40
msgid ""
"*Have a large library of ROMs to manage?* ROM Properties Page shell "
"extension is installed by default and makes it much easier, with thumbnails "
"and additional info for all of your files"
msgstr ""

#: getTips.go:89
msgid ""
"*Install a game with Lutris?* Right click on it and `Create steam shortcut` "
"to easily play it in 󰓓 Steam game mode."
msgstr ""
"Si vous installez un jeu avec Lutris, il suffit de faire un clic droit et "
"sélectionner `Create steam shortcut` pour le lancer facilement depuis le 󰓓 "
"Steam game mode."

#: getTips.go:36
msgid ""
"*Installing a Windows game that isn't on Steam?* Lutris is pre-installed and "
"recommended for better handling of wine prefixes ~ [View gaming guide](%s)"
msgstr ""
"Nous recommandons Lutris pour jouer à des jeux Windows qui ne sont pas "
"disponibles sur Steam. N'hésitez pas à regarder [le guide officiel] (%s)"

#: getTips.go:92
msgid ""
"*Looking for more security?* Tailscale and OpenVPN are built in, and can be "
"controlled from 󰓓 Steam game mode by the `Tailscale Control` and "
"`TunnelDeck` Decky loader plugins."
msgstr ""

#: getTips.go:64
msgid ""
"*Looking for some nostalgia?* Enable `Compiz windows effect` from the "
"Extension Manager."
msgstr ""

#: getTips.go:38
msgid "*Looking to setup Waydroid?* ~ [View our documentation](%s)"
msgstr ""

#: getTips.go:65
msgid ""
"*Missing the top left hot corner?* Apply pressure to the bottom edge of your "
"screen with your mouse. You can also re-enable the hot corner from settings "
"if desired."
msgstr ""

#: getTips.go:67
msgid ""
"*Need more control over your Flatpak apps permissions?* Check out [Flatseal]"
"(%s) to manage them."
msgstr ""
"*Besoin de plus de contrôle sur vos applis Flatpaks?* Installez [Flatseal]"
"(%s) pour les gérer"

#: getTips.go:58
msgid ""
"*Need more control over your Flatpak apps permissions?* Check out the \"App "
"permissions\" settings under the \"Security and privacy\" panel in the "
"system settings"
msgstr ""
"*Besoin de plus de contrôle sur vos applis Flatpaks?* Ouvrez l'appli "
"\"Configuration du système\", et dans la section \"Sécurité et "
"Confidentialité\", vous trouverez alors l'onglet \"Permission des "
"applications\""

#: getTips.go:112
msgid ""
"*Need to manage your Flatpak repositories and data?* Check out [Warehouse]"
"(%s) to manage them"
msgstr ""
"*Besoin de plus de contrôle sur les sources et les données de vos "
"applications Flatpak?*  Installez [Warehouse](%s) pour les gérer"

#: getTips.go:110
msgid ""
"*No Flatpak or distro packaging available?* The Gear Lever app is included "
"to make managing and integrating AppImages easy! ~ [Install it here](%s)"
msgstr ""
"Si l'appli que vous cherchez n'est pas disponible en paquet ou en Flatpak / "
"sur Bazaar, vous pouvez toujours télécharger la version AppImages et les "
"gérer facilement avec l'appli Gear Lever! ~ [Installez-la ici](%s)"

#: getTips.go:33
msgid ""
"*Update break something?* You can roll back and pin the previous release or "
"rebase by build date ~ [View our guide](%s)"
msgstr ""

#: getTips.go:93
msgid ""
"*Using a handheld that doesn't have enough buttons?* 󰓓 Steam game mode now "
"supports touch gestures to slide out the menus, thanks to [ChimeraOS](%s)"
msgstr ""

#: getTips.go:63
msgid ""
"*Want to control your device from your phone?* The GSConnect extension works "
"with your KDE Connect app ! [More info](%s)"
msgstr ""

#: getTips.go:56
msgid ""
"*Want to control your device from your phone?* The KDE Connect app functions "
"with all images ~ [More info](%s)"
msgstr ""

#: getTips.go:57
msgid ""
"*Want to customize and theme your desktop?* Tweak your desktop by following "
"our guide ~ [More info](%s)"
msgstr ""

#: getTips.go:87
msgid ""
"*Want to install Decky Loader?* There's a `ujust` command for that! `ujust "
"setup-decky install`"
msgstr ""

#: getTips.go:37
msgid ""
"BTRFS is used by default for internal drives, and we recommend BTRFS for "
"external drives including MicroSD cards. *NTFS and exFAT are not supported.*"
msgstr ""

#: getTips.go:39
msgid ""
"Bazzite uses ZSTD compression in BTRFS by default, and deduplicates files "
"across your entire drive. **More space for your games!**"
msgstr ""

